name: Ms.Mae713
review: Love the grip, the color. Good travel size.

review: Great tweezers! Paint doesn't chip off like they may on cheaper ones. Love the little case, great so I don't accidentally stab myself with them in my makeup bag. The high precision one is my favorite!

review: These are great for the eyebrows.

name: Just Me
review: Works well to remove those thin eye brows

review: Love the travel size and works well. It gets every single last eyebrow hair.

review: Very nice little set.  Love how compact and fits in my makeup bag at home and in my purse.  So far they work well.

review: These are my favorite brand of tweezers.

review: The price for two different style tweezers plus a pouch for easy travel makes this a must buy! I use the slant tip tweezers for stray facial hair and can use the pointed tweezers for my brows with absolute ease!

review: Tweezers are thin, sharp & pointed like I like.  Easy to get under eyebrows.

review: Helped pull out short hair but at the sa me time they are so sharp they would end up cutting hair instead of pull it out.
